result:
<st-modal
  title="成员变更"
  v-model="show"
  width="760px"
  @cancel="show = false"
>
  <st-form :form="form">
    <st-form-item labelGutter="12px" label="购卡人" required>
      <a-input
        :value="info.member_name + ' ' + info.mobile"
        :disabled="true"
        placeholder="请输入购卡人姓名"
      ></a-input>
    </st-form-item>
    <st-form-item labelGutter="12px" label="卡成员" required class="mg-b0">
      <add-card-member
        v-if="info && info.sale_range"
        v-model="list"
        :max="info.support_member_num - 1"
        :type="2"
      ></add-card-member>
    </st-form-item>
  </st-form>
  <template slot="footer">
    <st-button
      @click="changeCardMember"
      :loading="loading.changeCardMember"
      type="primary"
    >
      确认提交
    </st-button>
  </template>
</st-modal>
